title: Spectacular 2 Story home on oversized lot
posting_body: ['Found your dream home in the perfect neighborhood, but not quite ready to buy at this time?', 'Saving for a down payment or working on your credit can be difficult & it takes time.', 'Maybe you just moved here, and want to get to know the city before you commit to buying a home.', 'Call me to learn more about a program that allows you to select a home that is for sale, rent it, and have the right to buy that home at any time for a pre-set price.', 'We have helped thousands of people nationwide.', "I'd love to help you too!", 'Maria Martinez', 'show contact info', 'JPAR Realtors & Asscts', 'This home is an example of the great homes available.', 'We have helped thousands of people nationwide.', 'Certain terms and conditions apply.', 'ASK ME ABOUT MY RENTER TO HOMEOWNER PROGRAM!', 'I will pay your Lease Termination Fees!!!!', 'Free credit repair consulting available!']
